WEBVTT

01:00:02.000 --> 01:00:02.039
<b><font color='#fed64e'>BEEP</c></b>

01:00:10.239 --> 01:00:14.880
<b><font color='#fed64e'>Yes, my father did
work in that godforsaken house.</c></b>

01:00:16.599 --> 01:00:19.079
<b><font color='#fed64e'>He was head of
the hospital back then.</c></b>

01:00:20.320 --> 01:00:23.360
<b><font color='#fed64e'>I was very little,
but I remember glimpses of it.</c></b>

01:00:24.039 --> 01:00:27.840
<b><font color='#fed64e'>And it's no coincidence
that Sarah was at that house.</c></b>

01:00:33.599 --> 01:00:37.199
<b><font color='#fed64e'>It was about half a year ago.</c></b>
<b><font color='#fed64e'>She came to visit.</c></b>

01:00:37.840 --> 01:00:41.480
<b><font color='#fed64e'>I could tell right away
that something was very wrong.</c></b>

01:00:42.679 --> 01:00:45.320
<b><font color='#fed64e'>It didn't take much prodding.</c></b>

01:00:46.920 --> 01:00:50.880
<b><font color='#fed64e'>Apparently she
owed money, a lot of it,</c></b>

01:00:52.559 --> 01:00:55.199
<b><font color='#fed64e'>to some very</c></b>
<b><font color='#fed64e'> scary people.</c></b>

01:00:57.280 --> 01:00:58.920
<b><font color='#fed64e'>I told her not to worry.</c></b>

01:00:59.400 --> 01:01:04.519
<b><font color='#fed64e'>"Move out here," I said. "Start
a fresh." "I'll settle all your debts.</c></b>

01:01:04.679 --> 01:01:08.000
<b><font color='#fed64e'>I mean, what am I
going to do with all this?"</c></b>

01:01:10.480 --> 01:01:12.719
<b><font color='#fed64e'>But she wouldn't have it.</c></b>

01:01:13.320 --> 01:01:16.079
<b><font color='#fed64e'>She was a good girl at heart.</c></b>

01:01:16.920 --> 01:01:21.480
<b><font color='#fed64e'>Hated seeing me sell my
inheritance to pay her debts.</c></b>

01:01:23.920 --> 01:01:25.400
<b><font color='#fed64e'>But I could
tell it was serious.</c></b>

01:01:28.079 --> 01:01:34.320
<b><font color='#fed64e'>And so I lost my
good sense, fool that I am.</c></b>

01:01:36.440 --> 01:01:40.119
<b><font color='#fed64e'>"There may be
another way," I said.</c></b>

01:01:43.280 --> 01:01:46.159
<b><font color='#fed64e'>"I held my tongue for decades,</c></b>

01:01:46.760 --> 01:01:52.239
<b><font color='#fed64e'>but it was so hard</c></b>
<b><font color='#fed64e'>to see her suffer so</c></b>

01:01:52.400 --> 01:01:54.360
<b><font color='#fed64e'>much good </c></b>
<b><font color='#fed64e'>did that to her."</c></b>

01:01:59.239 --> 01:02:02.159
<b><font color='#fed64e'>My father was a
very successful man,</c></b>

01:02:02.960 --> 01:02:05.199
<b><font color='#fed64e'>as was his father before him.</c></b>

01:02:07.159 --> 01:02:09.480
<b><font color='#fed64e'>As the war drew nearer,</c></b>

01:02:09.920 --> 01:02:12.639
<b><font color='#fed64e'>my parents only realized </c></b>
<b><font color='#fed64e'>they would have to flee</c></b>

01:02:13.159 --> 01:02:16.039
<b><font color='#fed64e'>when it was almost too late.</c></b>

01:02:16.800 --> 01:02:21.239
<b><font color='#fed64e'>It certainly wasn't possible </c></b>
<b><font color='#fed64e'>to get out any amount of wealth.</c></b>

01:02:21.679 --> 01:02:23.519
<b><font color='#fed64e'>The noose had tightened.</c></b>

01:02:24.320 --> 01:02:26.880
<b><font color='#fed64e'>We were lucky to
get out with our lives.</c></b>

01:02:29.679 --> 01:02:32.480
<b><font color='#fed64e'>But my father
wasn't going to leave at all.</c></b>

01:02:34.800 --> 01:02:37.559
<b><font color='#fed64e'>He bought up lots of gold.</c></b>

01:02:39.480 --> 01:02:42.400
<b><font color='#fed64e'>People were
hiding their treasures</c></b>

01:02:42.599 --> 01:02:45.239
<b><font color='#fed64e'>in the walls and
the cellars of their houses.</c></b>

01:02:46.320 --> 01:02:48.480
<b><font color='#fed64e'>But my father
saw that wasn't safe,</c></b>

01:02:49.559 --> 01:02:51.639
<b><font color='#fed64e'>and he came up with a plan.</c></b>

01:02:53.119 --> 01:02:57.599
<b><font color='#fed64e'>"Hide it at the
hospital, in the Faust House."</c></b>

01:02:59.840 --> 01:03:01.119
<b><font color='#fed64e'>So we fled,</c></b>

01:03:02.519 --> 01:03:06.840
<b><font color='#fed64e'>first to London and
eventually to the States.</c></b>

01:03:07.519 --> 01:03:10.559
<b><font color='#fed64e'>My father got a job
at a hospital in Connecticut,</c></b>

01:03:12.519 --> 01:03:15.760
<b><font color='#fed64e'>and he never did get a
chance to go back for his wealth.</c></b>

01:03:17.960 --> 01:03:20.039
<b><font color='#fed64e'>Towards the end
he was a man possessed.</c></b>

01:03:21.679 --> 01:03:25.440
<b><font color='#fed64e'>"That's your wealth
hidden in that house," he said.</c></b>

01:03:26.000 --> 01:03:29.119
<b><font color='#fed64e'>"Your future hidden
in that house," he said.</c></b>

01:03:29.320 --> 01:03:32.920
<b><font color='#fed64e'>"Your future,
always the future."</c></b>

01:03:33.599 --> 01:03:34.880
<b><font color='#fed64e'>Ambition.</c></b>

01:03:36.400 --> 01:03:41.480
<b><font color='#fed64e'>I seem to be the only one
who doesn't have the obsession.</c></b>

01:03:46.039 --> 01:03:48.360
<b><font color='#fed64e'>I half-forgot the story.</c></b>

01:03:48.920 --> 01:03:53.440
<b><font color='#fed64e'>Something in me told me
I should take it to my grave,</c></b>

01:03:54.760 --> 01:03:58.360
<b><font color='#fed64e'>as of course
I should have done.</c></b>

01:04:00.360 --> 01:04:05.480
<b><font color='#fed64e'>After I told
Sara, she was changed.</c></b>

01:04:06.559 --> 01:04:08.480
<b><font color='#fed64e'>Soon after,</c></b>
<b><font color='#fed64e'>moved out here</c></b>

01:04:09.599 --> 01:04:12.239
<b><font color='#fed64e'>and got a job</c></b>
<b><font color='#fed64e'> in that house.</c></b>

01:04:16.000 --> 01:04:18.400
<b><font color='#fed64e'>I comforted myself.</c></b>

01:04:20.239 --> 01:04:23.039
<b><font color='#fed64e'>Thinking whatever</c></b>
<b><font color='#fed64e'> had been hidden there</c></b>

01:04:23.159 --> 01:04:25.800
<b><font color='#fed64e'>would surely</c></b>
<b><font color='#fed64e'>long be gone.</c></b>

01:04:26.760 --> 01:04:28.599
<b><font color='#fed64e'>She wouldn't find anything</c></b>

01:04:29.280 --> 01:04:34.079
<b><font color='#fed64e'>and eventually come to
her senses and accept my offer.</c></b>

01:04:35.280 --> 01:04:37.400
<b><font color='#fed64e'>But now I think...</c></b>